  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They've been drinking before, was before 12:00.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, I got summons to court.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The maximum penalty was $50.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took a solicitor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The court case and blah, blah, blah, blah, they let me free.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got the bill from the solicitor, 80, 80 pounds.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "With a maximum of 50 pounds, got 80 pounds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And so, you know, then I make a catering in there under supervision of beth din kosher catering-- had quite a lot of weddings.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then in '73, I think, I bought-- with the same partner, I bought a place-- we built a place called [?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Diane ?] Receptions.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was on Clarence Street, see, not far from here, quite a big place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they had quite a lot of wedding-- Jewish weddings, some non-Jewish weddings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But was very hard still with this permit-- drinking permit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it wasn't good-- doing good, that place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And finally, I bought out my partner.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I sold this business for lousy money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I could hardly buy a flat for this money what I got for this building-- standing still there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyhow, about the Schindler.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A friend of mine, Poldek Pfefferberg, Paul Page, we've been together in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He's from Cracow also.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I visit him in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I've been eight times in America to visit my brothers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I visited him in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he had on the counter a lot of photos and books and papers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He wanted to make a film but wasn't-- nobody was interested.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And one day by accident, Thomas Keneally, the writer of the or came by accident in Los Angeles to that shop, had broken travel case.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While he was waiting, he said, where you come from?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, from Australia.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
